OL,3,C#1.5bn in extra funding for military
OL,4,Chomes as part of defence review `
OL,5,CHealey
OL,7,FMore than #1.5 billion in extra
OL,8,Ffunding for military homes will be
OL,9,Fconfirmed as part of the Government's
OL,10,Fstrategic defence review, the Ministry
OL,11,Fof Defence has said.
OL,13,FThe review, expected soon, will set
OL,14,Fout the money, which will be put
OL,15,Ftowards work to improve housing and
OL,16,Funlock further development.
OL,18,FCash will be used on urgent repairs
OL,19,Fsuch as fixing boilers and roofs, and
OL,20,Fother issues including tackling damp,
OL,21,Fthe MoD said.
