OL,3,C#1.5bn in extra funding for military
OL,4,Chomes as part of defence review `
OL,5,CHealey
OL,7,FSpeaking on a visit to some military
OL,8,Fhomes in Cambridgeshire, Defence
OL,9,FSecretary John Healey said: "I'm
OL,10,Fannouncing through the strategic
OL,11,Fdefence review a record increase `
OL,12,F#1.5 billion in the next five years `
OL,13,Fto upgrade military family homes.
OL,15,F"Our forces make extraordinary
OL,16,Fsacrifices to keep us safe and to
OL,17,Fserve this country and yet for years,
OL,18,Fwe've forced their families to live in
OL,19,Fsubstandard homes that you or I ...
OL,20,Fjust wouldn't tolerate."
