OL,5,CHealey
OL,7,FHe also said the review will
OL,8,F"recognise the fact that the world is
OL,9,Fchanging, threats are increasing".
OL,11,F"In this new era of threat we need a
OL,12,Fnew era for defence."
OL,14,FIt will be "the vision and direction
OL,15,Ffor the way that we've got to
OL,16,Fstrengthen our armed forces to make us
OL,17,Fmore secure at home, stronger abroad",
OL,18,Fhe said.
