OL,3,C#1.5bn in extra funding for military
OL,4,Chomes as part of defence review `
OL,5,CHealey
OL,7,FThe strategic defence review was
OL,8,Flaunched by Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,9,FStarmer last year, as the Government
OL,10,Flooks to overhaul Britain's military
OL,11,Fin the face of rising global tensions.
OL,13,FAhead of the review, the UK has
OL,14,Falready committed to spend 2.5% of
OL,15,Fgross domestic product ` a measure of
OL,16,Fthe size of the economy ` on defence
OL,17,Ffrom April 2027, rising to 3% during
OL,18,Fthe next Parliament.
