OL,5,CHealey
OL,7,FLast month, the Government launched a
OL,8,Fconsumer charter aimed at improving
OL,9,Fthe living conditions for service
OL,10,Fpersonnel and their families.
OL,12,FIt commits to higher move-in
OL,13,Fstandards, more reliable repairs and a
OL,14,Fnamed housing officer for every family.
OL,16,FIt also pledges a shorter complaints
OL,17,Fprocess and more freedom for families
OL,18,Fto be able to make improvements to
OL,19,Ftheir service homes.
