OL,4,Chomes as part of defence review `
OL,5,CHealey
OL,7,FLiberal Democrat defence spokeswoman
OL,8,FHelen Maguire called on the Government
OL,9,Fto go further in its pledge, by
OL,10,Fbringing military accommodation up to
OL,11,Fthe decent homes standard ` the
OL,12,Fminimum standards that social homes
OL,13,Fshould meet.
OL,15,FShe said she was "glad to see this
OL,16,FGovernment has finally come to their
OL,17,Fsenses and listened", and added:
OL,18,F"Those bravely defending our country
OL,19,Fdeserve proper housing without leaks,
OL,20,Fmould, floods and freezing
OL,21,Ftemperatures.
